1
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:05,950
You're here.

2
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,790
I brought you some snacks.

3
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,190
No need.

4
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:12,160
I don't have much of an appetite.

5
00:02:13,190 --> 00:02:14,850
Why don't you go back and rest?

6
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,630
You are already so exhausted.

7
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:18,190
I still have 2 medical books to read.

8
00:02:18,190 --> 00:02:18,800
Tomorrow.

9
00:02:27,590 --> 00:02:29,120
You can read them tomorrow.

10
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:31,560
You don't need to worry about me.

11
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,030
There's a small bed inside.

12
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,760
I can rest there when I'm tired.

13
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:37,000
You're a woman.

14
00:02:37,079 --> 00:02:38,030
This won't do.

15
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:41,840
Why won't it do?

16
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,400
It's really nice.

17
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,960
Let me show you.

18
00:02:56,470 --> 00:02:57,280
Look.

19
00:02:58,430 --> 00:02:59,630
You're sleeping here?

20
00:02:59,630 --> 00:03:00,630
This won't do.

21
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:02,190
Why not?

22
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:04,400
Of course, it's not as comfortable
as the mansion,

23
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,530
but it's enough for an occasional nap.

24
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,680
In this case,

25
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,290
I'll stay and keep you company.

26
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,630
You just recovered not long ago.

27
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,630
Pushing yourself like this,

28
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,230
I'm worried you'll relapse.

29
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,800
I'm fine.

30
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:22,200
This is much better
than the military camp.

31
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,370
Then I won't insist.

32
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,710
If you're tired, rest here for a while.

33
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:27,240
Okay.

34
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,000
What's wrong?

35
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,690
Are you feeling unwell?

36
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:36,900
No.

37
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,960
Maybe I haven't rested well
the past couple of days.

38
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,820
I'll be fine after a little sleep.

39
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,400
Are you really okay?

40
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,150
Yes.

41
00:03:43,430 --> 00:03:44,760
Go ahead with your work.

42
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:55,400
I didn't expect that he still keeps it.

43
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,680
Physician Han.

44
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,270
Something terrible has happened.

45
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:18,000
His Majesty's condition
has suddenly worsened.

46
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,360
Please go and treat him immediately.

47
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,070
What?

48
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,070
How could this be?

49
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:22,070
I don't know.

50
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:23,130
I'll go right away.

51
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,000
I'll go with you.

52
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,480
Okay.

53
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,630
His Majesty has not had any food

54
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,630
or water for days.

55
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:33,950
If this continues,

56
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,600
how can his body endure it?

57
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:37,630
We've tried every possible method,

58
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,480
but the results have been very limited.

59
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,430
What should we do?

60
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:41,720
Indeed.

61
00:05:42,270 --> 00:05:43,360
Prescribe some more tonics.

62
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,830
Okay.

63
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:45,960
Let me check His Majesty's condition.

64
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,160
How is it?

65
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,270
His Majesty's pulse is weak.

66
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,240
We must find the cause

67
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,370
of his nightmares as soon as possible.

68
00:06:39,190 --> 00:06:39,720
This is...

69
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,780
Don't come closer.

70
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:44,860
I need to cut it out.

71
00:06:45,430 --> 00:06:46,040
Cut?

72
00:06:47,390 --> 00:06:48,070
Physician Han,

73
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:48,800
you can't do this.

74
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,000
How can you use a knife

75
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:50,680
on His Majesty's body?

76
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,070
Please think twice, Physician Han.

77
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,400
If anything goes wrong,

78
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,420
I will bear full responsibility.

79
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,630
Look...

80
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:26,750
What is it?

81
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:28,070
Right, worms.

82
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:34,870
Jin Xi.

83
00:07:37,310 --> 00:07:38,600
Jin Xi!

84
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,630
Your Highness.

85
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,560
Jin Xi didn't enter the palace.

86
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,040
Your Highness.

87
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,830
Even if you don't consider yourself,

88
00:07:52,830 --> 00:07:55,070
you must consider the child
you're carrying.

89
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,920
The floor is cold.

90
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,920
Let me help you up.

91
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,680
Is His Majesty better?

92
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,240
There is no news yet.

93
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,830
There are still many guards

94
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,890
outside our Noble Consort Pavilion.

95
00:08:32,669 --> 00:08:34,030
Help me send this out.

96
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,210
Find Physician Han.

97
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,750
Find Lord Fei

98
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,870
and tell him he must come see me.

99
00:08:54,840 --> 00:08:57,390
Did I really harm Liu Chu?

100
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,240
That's too reckless.

101
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:05,200
If anything happens to His Majesty,

102
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:07,240
your entire family will be executed.

103
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,840
My family is already gone.

104
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,150
The situation was urgent.

105
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,240
If we don't treat
His Majesty immediately,

106
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,390
he will be in danger.

107
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,150
And you, General Xiao.

108
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:16,240
Holding a weapon in the hall

109
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:18,480
is a crime of profound disrespect.

110
00:09:19,750 --> 00:09:22,360
The Eldest Princess has arrived.

111
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,270
Greetings, Your Highness.

112
00:09:24,270 --> 00:09:26,480
Greetings, Your Highness.

113
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,550
You may all rise.

114
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:30,150
What happened?

115
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:33,270
Physician Han and General Xiao
are harming the Emperor's body,

116
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:35,800
showing profound disrespect
to His Majesty.

117
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,150
Your Highness,

118
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,840
His Majesty was poisoned by Gu.

119
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,600
That is why

120
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,480
the cause of his illness
couldn't be found.

121
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,030
Now that the Gu worm has been removed,

122
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:44,240
please rest assured.

123
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,390
If, as Physician Han said,

124
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,750
you and General Xiao did this

125
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,270
to save His Majesty,

126
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,840
then naturally I will not
pursue the matter.

127
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:55,300
Thank you, Your Highness.

128
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:56,910
No need for formalities.

129
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:58,630
The top priority now

130
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:00,750
is to wake His Majesty
up as soon as possible.

131
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,280
I will certainly do my best.

132
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:05,870
That explains

133
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,150
why we couldn't diagnose
His Majesty's illness all this time.

134
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:09,840
it turns out he was poisoned by Gu.

135
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,600
Well,

136
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,390
why do you seem relieved?

137
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,240
You don't know this.

138
00:10:14,670 --> 00:10:16,360
Uncle Lie has done a lot of research

139
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,390
on the Gu poison of Changmo.

140
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:18,870
He previously developed

141
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,240
a special pill

142
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,300
that can be used to ward off Gu poison.

143
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,440
Then Chu is saved.

144
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,480
Exactly.

145
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:32,410
May the ancestors of Changmo bless

146
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:35,440
Liu Chu to wake up safely.

147
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,860
If we can survive this ordeal,

148
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,680
I am willing to spend the rest of my life

149
00:10:43,030 --> 00:10:45,240
in exchange for his well-being

150
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,670
and peace between the two lands.

151
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,080
Your Highness,

152
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,270
Lord Fei is here.

153
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:59,070
Please ask him to come in.

154
00:11:09,030 --> 00:11:09,890
Your Highness,

155
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
you summoned me.

156
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:11,790
Lord Fei,

157
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:14,200
how is Liu Chu?

158
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:18,830
His condition is still the same.

159
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,600
He still hasn't woken up.

160
00:11:21,240 --> 00:11:22,870
General Xiao and Physician Han

161
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:24,470
have been trying their best.

162
00:11:26,030 --> 00:11:26,870
That's good.

163
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:29,340
Physician Han is highly skilled.

164
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,440
She has many good remedies.

165
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:33,760
She can definitely save Liu Chu.

166
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,610
Is there anything else I can do for him?

167
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,460
Your Highness,

168
00:11:39,720 --> 00:11:40,550
all you can do now

169
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:43,150
is take care of yourself
and your unborn child.

170
00:11:43,870 --> 00:11:45,670
Please don't worry too much

171
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,680
and harm the imperial child.

172
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,600
I know.

173
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,040
Consort Ling,

174
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:53,160
I shouldn't stay here long,

175
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:54,620
so I will take my leave.

176
00:11:54,790 --> 00:11:55,750
Please

177
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,960
remember what I just said.

178
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,570
Thank you, Lord Fei.

179
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,370
I will take my leave.

180
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,840
Why are you only here now?

181
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,600
Greetings, Your Highness.

182
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,480
Are you sure this antidote works?

183
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,720
There's no other choice

184
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,790
but to give it a try.

185
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,610
If anything happens to His Majesty...

186
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:14,600
What's wrong?

187
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,930
What's wrong with him?

188
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,020
Let's wait and see.

189
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,870
Xie.

190
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:19,720
I'm here.

191
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:20,480
Xie.

192
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,280
Your Majesty.

193
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:23,030
I'm here.

194
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:27,030
Your Majesty.

195
00:13:27,200 --> 00:13:28,150
Liu Chu.

196
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:29,600
Liu Chu.

197
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:30,840
Liu Chu.

198
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,870
Your Majesty.

199
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:40,630
This...

200
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,270
How is that possible?

201
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:47,000
His Majesty...

202
00:13:48,150 --> 00:13:49,550
His Majesty...

203
00:13:51,870 --> 00:13:53,200
has stopped breathing.

204
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:55,870
Your Majesty!

205
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:59,630
Your Majesty!

206
00:13:59,630 --> 00:14:01,320
How is that possible?

207
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:03,360
Your Majesty!

208
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,480
Your Majesty!

209
00:14:04,600 --> 00:14:06,730
How could you just pass away like this?

210
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,360
What happened?

211
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:16,440
Enough!

212
00:14:17,750 --> 00:14:18,550
Guards!

213
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,440
Take Han Yunling and Xiao Chi

214
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,670
to the Imperial Prison.

215
00:14:21,670 --> 00:14:22,440
Yes.

216
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,960
Move.

217
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,240
Pass my order.

218
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:42,360
Close the palace gates from today.

219
00:14:42,870 --> 00:14:44,440
No one is allowed to leave.

220
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,080
If anyone spreads the news

221
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,410
of His Majesty's death,

222
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,480
I will execute their entire family!

223
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,000
Yes.

224
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:52,000
Get lost!

225
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,630
Your Highness,

226
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:08,150
His Majesty has passed away.

227
00:15:08,670 --> 00:15:09,960
What should we do?

228
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,480
Your Highness,

229
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:16,010
you are the only descendant
of the Liu family.

230
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:18,320
You are now the sole ruler of Jinglan.

231
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,480
At this time,

232
00:15:20,910 --> 00:15:22,840
we cannot be indecisive.

233
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,670
You may leave.

234
00:15:26,150 --> 00:15:26,960
Yes.

235
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,000
Xie.

236
00:15:45,870 --> 00:15:46,670
Xie.

237
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:48,870
You are smart and wise.

238
00:15:49,790 --> 00:15:53,480
But Liu Chu is innocent and naive.

239
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:56,750
You must manage the treasury well

240
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,030
and assist Liu Chu.

241
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,750
The kingdom of Jinglan

242
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:05,270
is now in your hands.

243
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:05,840
Father.

244
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,870
I will definitely take good care of Chu.

245
00:16:07,870 --> 00:16:09,360
I promise.

246
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,120
Okay.

247
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:16,240
Father!

248
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:19,440
Your Majesty!

249
00:16:21,240 --> 00:16:23,030
Is this the will of Heaven?

250
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,030
His Majesty has passed away.

251
00:16:25,030 --> 00:16:27,000
Jinglan will inevitably fall into chaos.

252
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:29,660
The court ministers
will surely be leaderless—

253
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:32,170
only you can step forward and take charge.

254
00:16:32,550 --> 00:16:33,480
For Jinglan,

255
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,540
and for the people,

256
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,700
please follow the will of Heaven.

257
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:42,360
Follow the will of Heaven?

258
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:49,030
What should we do?

259
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:50,870
This is so sudden.

260
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:53,730
The state cannot be
without a ruler for a single day.

261
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:57,520
What are you all arguing about?

262
00:16:59,240 --> 00:17:01,030
Lord Zhang and Lord Li are here.

263
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:02,480
Every single one of you

264
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:04,440
is an important minister of the court.

265
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:07,349
Making such a racket in this hall—

266
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,680
How inappropriate!

267
00:17:11,030 --> 00:17:11,790
Exactly.

268
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:13,240
How inappropriate!

269
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:15,349
In this court,

270
00:17:15,510 --> 00:17:16,960
with Lord Zhang here,

271
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,790
Jinglan will not fall into chaos.

272
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:20,440
That may be true,

273
00:17:20,440 --> 00:17:22,880
but His Majesty's fate is unknown.

274
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,790
How can we not panic?

275
00:17:24,790 --> 00:17:26,480
Yes, right.

276
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,880
If His Majesty really passes away,

277
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:56,790
wouldn't Jinglan be left without a leader?

278
00:17:56,790 --> 00:18:00,160
Wouldn't the Liu Family have no successor?

279
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:02,400
Even if His Majesty passes away,

280
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:04,270
we have to accept it.

281
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:06,480
The main question is what we should do.

282
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:08,030
What should Jinglan do?

283
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:09,830
Without the Liu Family ruling the world,

284
00:18:09,830 --> 00:18:12,480
could our great Jinglan really perish?

285
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,400
What you said makes sense.

286
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:15,400
But Liu Chu

287
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,880
doesn't have the ability
to govern Jinglan after all.

288
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:19,880
It's the same with or without him.

289
00:18:19,880 --> 00:18:21,480
Even if he dies,

290
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,960
aren't Lord Zhang
and Lord Li still there?

291
00:18:23,960 --> 00:18:26,000
Jinglan won't be in chaos.

292
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:27,110
Yes.

293
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:28,590
We have Lord Zhang and Lord Li.

294
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:30,030
Lord Zhang.

295
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,070
Look,

296
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:34,030
this is what the people want.

297
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:36,240
Yes, Lord Zhang.

298
00:18:36,350 --> 00:18:38,080
Jinglan cannot do without you.

299
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:41,030
My fellow ministers,

300
00:18:41,030 --> 00:18:43,240
are you forcing me

301
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:45,570
to become an eternal traitor to the realm?

302
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,640
Lord Zhang.

303
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,110
The common people

304
00:18:49,110 --> 00:18:52,590
will engrave your achievements
on a monument

305
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:55,030
for generations to come.

306
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:57,110
Yes.

307
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,640
I cannot do it!

308
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,240
Lord Zhang, this is
what everyone expects of you.

309
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,030
I cannot do it!

310
00:19:01,030 --> 00:19:01,720
Lord Zhang.

311
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:02,880
Yes.

312
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,680
I cannot do it!

313
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,070
Lord Zhang.

314
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:08,390
The Liu Family hasn't
completely died out yet.

315
00:19:13,350 --> 00:19:15,590
You are indeed a member of the Liu Family.

316
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:18,640
But you are a woman.

317
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:19,750
Since ancient times,

318
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:22,440
there has never been a precedent
for a woman to be an emperor.

319
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,160
That's right.

320
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:25,270
Your Highness
has managed the treasury for many years

321
00:19:25,270 --> 00:19:27,200
and indeed has a talent for finance.

322
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,790
But when it comes to ruling the country

323
00:19:28,790 --> 00:19:30,440
and leading the ministers—

324
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,400
well,

325
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:33,030
who would truly accept your authority?

326
00:19:33,030 --> 00:19:34,480
Yes.

327
00:19:36,550 --> 00:19:38,830
You were all promoted
by the late emperor

328
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:41,430
to reach your current positions,
weren't you?

329
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:42,790
Each one of you has enjoyed
wealth, honor,

330
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:44,640
and power for years,

331
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:47,080
yet not a shred of gratitude do you have.

332
00:19:49,480 --> 00:19:50,880
A couple of insolent buffoons,

333
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,200
nobodies,

334
00:19:52,200 --> 00:19:54,440
daring to disrupt
the imperial court's order?

335
00:19:54,440 --> 00:19:55,160
Guards!

336
00:19:55,480 --> 00:19:57,400
Take them away
and execute them on the spot.

337
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,160
Yes!

338
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:59,110
Lord Zhang.

339
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,030
Lord Zhang, we are innocent! Lord Zhang!

340
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:01,690
Lord Zhang.

341
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:02,920
Lord Zhang, we are innocent!

342
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,510
Lord Zhang, we are innocent!

343
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,640
Save us, Lord Zhang.

344
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:07,040
Who else dares to object?

345
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,880
Lord Zhang!

346
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:11,030
We are innocent!

347
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,880
Lord Zhang.

348
00:20:14,830 --> 00:20:16,510
I am here.

349
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:18,590
You are a veteran official.

350
00:20:19,030 --> 00:20:20,960
If your legs and feet are not nimble,

351
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:23,200
I will have someone
bring a cushion for you

352
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:25,730
and grant you the honor
of sitting in the hall.

353
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:27,350
What do you think?

354
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,200
I

355
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:31,160
thank Your Highness.

356
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:32,510
Li Shichang.

357
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:34,790
I am here.

358
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,830
Do you think in this court,

359
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:39,880
there is anyone other than me, Liu Xie,

360
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,740
more suitable for this position?

361
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,240
Naturally, the Liu Family's empire

362
00:20:44,240 --> 00:20:46,510
should be ruled by the Liu Family.

363
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:49,030
Your Highness, although you are a woman,

364
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,880
in terms of talent and ability,

365
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:53,310
you are no less than any man in the court.

366
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:54,200
If—

367
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:56,030
and I mean if—

368
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:58,970
something unfortunate happens
to His Majesty,

369
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:03,000
you are undeniably the one
to succeed the throne.

370
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:06,690
What do you think, Lord Zhang?

371
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,480
I have absolutely no objections.

372
00:21:10,480 --> 00:21:11,350
All right.

373
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:15,440
Since the two Chief Grand Secretaries
both say so,

374
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:18,920
Then I will not refuse.

375
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:20,060
Your Highness,

376
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:21,030
please.

377
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:41,350
Jinglan cannot be
without a ruler for a day.

378
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:43,000
His Majesty is currently unwell.

379
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,160
I, Liu Xie,

380
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,640
born into the royal family

381
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,240
and sharing the same blood
with His Majesty,

382
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,590
should shoulder

383
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:50,480
the responsibility
of maintaining the stability of the state,

384
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:52,940
to ensure the eternal prosperity
of Jinglan

385
00:21:53,030 --> 00:21:55,360
and the peace and happiness of the people.

386
00:21:59,270 --> 00:22:02,200
With Your Highness
ascending the throne,

387
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:04,960
Jinglan will surely prosper forever,

388
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,880
and the people will live in peace.

389
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:15,280
How could the morning court

390
00:22:18,030 --> 00:22:19,750
proceed without me?

391
00:22:21,240 --> 00:22:22,480
Your Majesty.

392
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,640
Your Majesty.

393
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:26,510
Your Majesty.

394
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:07,070
You may leave now.

395
00:23:07,070 --> 00:23:07,830
Yes.

396
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,480
Xiao Chi.

397
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:19,880
Did Chu really...

398
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:21,070
Chu isn't dead.

399
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,440
After Yunling removed the Gu worms

400
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:24,350
from his body,

401
00:23:24,550 --> 00:23:26,950
Chu decided
to play along with their trick.

402
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,880
You guys are too bold.

403
00:23:31,270 --> 00:23:32,480
What if something happened to him—

404
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:33,640
He had planned this

405
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,640
since he fell ill.

406
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:38,880
I see.

407
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,830
Only by spreading the news
of His Majesty's death

408
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,000
can those with ulterior motives

409
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,330
show their true colors.

410
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:47,880
Then we can completely
eradicate hidden dangers

411
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,740
and consolidate imperial power.

412
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:53,350
This is the medicine His Majesty needs
for his recovery.

413
00:23:53,350 --> 00:23:54,950
Please take it out, Lord Fei.

414
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,000
Rest assured.

415
00:23:58,240 --> 00:23:59,070
I'll go right now.

416
00:23:59,070 --> 00:23:59,640
Zheng.

417
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:01,640
This is a matter of great importance.

418
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:03,300
The only ones Chu can trust now

419
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,030
are you and me.

420
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,030
I, Fei Zheng,

421
00:24:08,790 --> 00:24:10,920
will make sure he takes this medicine.

422
00:24:31,030 --> 00:24:32,890
Offer the Eldest Princess a seat.

423
00:24:37,030 --> 00:24:37,960
Your Majesty.

424
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,370
Are you going to pass the throne

425
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:42,880
to the Eldest Princess?

426
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:43,960
Xie,

427
00:24:43,960 --> 00:24:45,030
Father is going to pass the throne to you.

428
00:24:45,030 --> 00:24:46,030
I do have this idea.

429
00:24:46,030 --> 00:24:47,230
Don't talk nonsense.

430
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:50,880
She is indeed outstanding.

431
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:51,880
But Your Majesty,

432
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:56,000
do you know
what "eating an heirless household" means?

433
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:57,830
"Eating an heirless household"?

434
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:58,550
Yes.

435
00:24:58,790 --> 00:25:00,190
Among the common people,

436
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:02,070
if there is no male in the family

437
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:03,790
and only women are left,

438
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,240
the family's property

439
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,440
will be divided by other relatives

440
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,880
and villagers in the clan.

441
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:11,160
Your Majesty, you have a prince,

442
00:25:11,160 --> 00:25:13,750
but you intend to pass
the throne to the Princess.

443
00:25:13,750 --> 00:25:14,880
First,

444
00:25:15,030 --> 00:25:16,790
it does not conform
to the ancestral system.

445
00:25:16,790 --> 00:25:17,880
Second,

446
00:25:17,880 --> 00:25:20,790
the throne is easily coveted.

447
00:25:26,640 --> 00:25:28,350
Passing His Majesty's oral decree:

448
00:25:28,350 --> 00:25:30,400
When I was ill,

449
00:25:30,590 --> 00:25:32,640
all ministers worked diligently

450
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:34,170
and exhausted their minds.

451
00:25:34,200 --> 00:25:35,750
You are all meritorious.

452
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:36,640
Today,

453
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:39,160
I decide to open the treasury

454
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:41,920
and grant all ministers 3 years' salary.

455
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,640
By Imperial Command.

456
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:50,160
We obey Your Majesty's edict.

457
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:54,400
Long live Your Majesty.

458
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:58,030
My ministers,

459
00:25:58,480 --> 00:25:59,440
you may rise.

460
00:26:00,750 --> 00:26:03,200
Thank you, Your Majesty.

461
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,830
Your Majesty,

462
00:26:09,830 --> 00:26:12,270
this seems a bit inappropriate.

463
00:26:12,480 --> 00:26:15,270
As long as Your Majesty returns safely.

464
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,720
This reward

465
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:19,070
is quite a large expense.

466
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:20,000
Lord Zhang.

467
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:23,350
What's wrong with His Majesty
rewarding loyal subjects?

468
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:25,440
Besides, you're also a loyal subject.

469
00:26:25,440 --> 00:26:26,240
His Majesty

470
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:28,070
will also reward you.

471
00:26:28,880 --> 00:26:31,880
Please see clearly, Your Majesty.

472
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:35,880
Zhang Ruizhong
is no loyal subject, either,

473
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,830
Your Majesty.

474
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:37,680
Lord Li,

475
00:26:38,160 --> 00:26:40,590
what nonsense are you talking about?

476
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,520
Zhang Ruizhong,

477
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,440
don't play dumb with me.

478
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:43,880
You—

479
00:26:44,070 --> 00:26:45,200
Your Majesty,

480
00:26:45,350 --> 00:26:48,270
he has a dragon robe hidden in his house.

481
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:51,640
He has long harbored the intention
to usurp the throne,

482
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:54,270
Your Majesty.

483
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,070
Xiao Chi.

484
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:56,240
I am here.

485
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,310
Investigate.

486
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,850
I accept the decree.

487
00:27:07,590 --> 00:27:09,120
What else do you have to say?

488
00:27:09,270 --> 00:27:10,270
Your Majesty,

489
00:27:10,270 --> 00:27:13,030
I have truly never seen this thing before.

490
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:15,070
I really haven't seen it.

491
00:27:15,070 --> 00:27:15,920
Lord Zhang.

492
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:18,030
I searched this out myself.

493
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:20,000
How could I be wronging you?

494
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,160
General Xiao.

495
00:27:21,350 --> 00:27:23,200
How is this possible?

496
00:27:24,030 --> 00:27:27,070
These books are the sole surviving copies

497
00:27:27,070 --> 00:27:29,400
of ancient texts from various dynasties.

498
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:30,880
Your Majesty.

499
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:33,070
Years ago, I went
to Lord Zhang's house for his birthday.

500
00:27:33,070 --> 00:27:34,030
He got drunk

501
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:36,240
and said he had a dragon robe hidden.

502
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:38,750
He also said that one day
he would wear it,

503
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:39,750
sit on the dragon throne,

504
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:41,280
and lead the army in person.

505
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:44,480
At the time, I thought he was just drunk

506
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:45,550
and speaking happily—

507
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,480
I thought that's just a jest
made under the influence of wine.

508
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:47,400
Who would have thought

509
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,240
he really had

510
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:50,640
the intention to usurp
the throne, Your Majesty.

511
00:27:50,640 --> 00:27:51,640
Li Shichang!

512
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:53,480
What nonsense are you talking about?

513
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:54,880
Nonsense?

514
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:55,680
Looking at it this way,

515
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:57,350
who's behind His Majesty’s illness

516
00:27:57,350 --> 00:27:59,000
is still unknown.

517
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,270
Your Majesty.

518
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:02,680
Li Shichang is framing me!

519
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:04,440
He is really framing me!

520
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:06,240
Please see clearly, Your Majesty.

521
00:28:06,240 --> 00:28:09,160
Li Shichang, you bastard!

522
00:28:09,880 --> 00:28:10,830
Zhang Ruizhong.

523
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:12,070
Words are not proof.

524
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,550
This dragon robe is ironclad evidence,

525
00:28:14,550 --> 00:28:16,440
Your Majesty!

526
00:28:16,440 --> 00:28:17,880
I am innocent!

527
00:28:17,880 --> 00:28:19,110
I am innocent!

528
00:28:19,110 --> 00:28:20,040
Zhang Ruizhong!

529
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:23,030
As the Chief Minister,

530
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:26,430
I should have executed your entire family.

531
00:28:27,270 --> 00:28:30,470
But considering you assisted
the late Emperor for years,

532
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:32,270
I will spare your life.

533
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:33,510
From now on,

534
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:36,000
you are grounded at home

535
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,270
and must never leave!

536
00:28:37,400 --> 00:28:38,550
As for your family,

537
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:40,750
they shall all be beheaded!

538
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:44,160
I am innocent, Your Majesty!

539
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:46,750
Your Majesty, I am innocent!

540
00:28:47,790 --> 00:28:48,790
Your Majesty.

541
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,790
Your Majesty!

542
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:52,960
Your Majesty!

543
00:28:52,960 --> 00:28:54,400
I am innocent!

544
00:28:54,400 --> 00:28:56,350
I am innocent!

545
00:28:56,350 --> 00:28:57,680
Your Majesty.

546
00:28:58,270 --> 00:29:02,030
I am innocent!

547
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:18,880
Why do I have no appetite?

548
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,880
You're all right.

549
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:36,640
I thought you would never come back.

550
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,790
During the time you were unconscious,

551
00:29:38,790 --> 00:29:40,350
I kept praying,

552
00:29:40,350 --> 00:29:43,270
wishing to exchange my life for yours.

553
00:29:48,160 --> 00:29:49,680
Now that I'm better,

554
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:52,440
do you have to pay with your life?

555
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,270
I'm kidding.

556
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,640
Here I am,

557
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:04,480
standing right in front of you,
alive and well.

558
00:30:04,480 --> 00:30:05,350
Don't worry.

559
00:30:06,270 --> 00:30:07,030
Come,

560
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:08,500
let's have a drink.

561
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,000
Somebody!

562
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:14,680
Bring some wine.

563
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:22,550
Your Majesty,

564
00:30:23,480 --> 00:30:24,240
I am pregnant.

565
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:25,270
I cannot drink.

566
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,480
Just a little bit.

567
00:30:28,240 --> 00:30:29,500
It won't hurt the baby.

568
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:31,920
Besides,

569
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:33,590
I just love drinking.

570
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:35,200
If it is really my child,

571
00:30:36,200 --> 00:30:36,830
then...

572
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:39,350
he should have liked drinking even

573
00:30:39,350 --> 00:30:41,070
when he was in the womb.

574
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,340
Aren't you going to say something

575
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:56,790
to congratulate me?

576
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:04,240
I congratulate Your Majesty

577
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,070
on your safe return.

578
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:07,880
Good.

579
00:31:20,590 --> 00:31:21,440
My love,

580
00:31:21,880 --> 00:31:24,010
there is one thing I cannot figure out.

581
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:25,350
Tell me,

